<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.1.1">
<l>muṭicōti yāyuṉatu mukaccōti malarntatuvō</l>
<l>vaṭicōti nīniṉṟa tāmaraiyā yalarntatuvō</l>
<l>paṭicōti yāṭaiyoṭum palkalaṉāy niṉpaimpoṉ</l>
<l>kaṭicōti kalantatuvō tirumālē kaṭṭuraiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Does the light of your face bloom as the light of a crown?</l>
<l>Does the light of [your] feet bloom as a lotus on which you stand?</l>
<l>Does your fresh golden protective light mingle</l>
<l>as many ornaments with your bright body garment? Tell [me]!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
